dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Arthur Campbell. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Olivia. Can you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's eight zero three two five.
Thank you, Olivia. I also need your date of birth to verify your identity. When were you born?
I was born on the twenty-second of May, nineteen ninety-four.
Great, thank you for the information. Is there anything specific you would like assistance with today regarding your policy?
I'm interested in adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Certainly, Olivia. I can help you with that. Let's get started with the details of the vehicle you would like to add.
Thank you for your time, Olivia. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
